arkness that causes the storms. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826790/extras/GIF-EXPLORE-COMPRESSED.gif?t=1739565893\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826790/extras/Stormforge_SectionTitle_GATHERCRAFTBUILD.png?t=1739565893\" /><br>Gather critical magical elements inside the storms to craft epic weapons, armor, and structures. Build up your base to withstand the power of the storms!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826790/extras/GIF-GATHER-COMPRESSED.gif?t=1739565893\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826790/extras/Stormforge_SectionTitle_GREATTOGETHER.png?t=1739565893\" /><br>Embark on an epic solo adventure or join with friends in 8 player co-op gameplay. Unlock unique and complementary powers that allow you to thrive as a team. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826790/extras/GIF-TOGETHER-COMPRESSED.gif?t=1739565893\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826790/extras/Stormforge_SectionTitle_MODS.png?t=1739565893\" /><br>Easily play with a wide variety of community created equipment, enemies, points of interest, and game rules. Choose to add mods into your existing game without any separate downloads.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826790/extras/GIF-MODS-COMPRESSED.gif?t=1739565893\" /><br><br>Immerse yourself in the storm-filled world of Sorana and experience a survival adventure like no other!<br><br><br><br>","developers":["Roboto Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RP